---
title: Double Garlic Chicken & Crouton Salad with Creamy Dressing & Almonds
description: Feeling fresh and reset or perhaps this is what you’ve been looking for. If that’s the case, there’s no better remedy for a stressful day than an easy dinner option like this garlic-infused chicken and crispy crouton salad. It will leave you feeling satisfied and light.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
